"关联文件： - @packages/agentsociety2/agentsociety2/backend/app.py - 主应用，注册此路由 "
"(/api/v1/prefill-params) - @extension/src/prefillParamsViewProvider.ts - "
"VSCode插件前端调用此API - @extension/src/webview/prefillParams/ - 前端展示组件"
msgstr ""
"Related files: - @packages/agentsociety2/agentsociety2/backend/app.py - "
"main application that registers this route (/api/v1/prefill-params) - "
"@extension/src/prefillParamsViewProvider.ts - VSCode extension frontend "
"that calls this API - @extension/src/webview/prefillParams/ - frontend "
"display components"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params:8 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "读取文件： - {workspace}/.agentsociety/prefill_params.json - 预填充参数配置"
msgstr ""
"Reads the following file: - {workspace}/.agentsociety/prefill_params.json"
" - prefill parameter configuration"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:1 of
msgid "获取全局预填充参数"
msgstr "Get global prefill parameters"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:3 of
msgid "返回工作区中所有类（Agent和环境模块）的预填充参数配置。"
msgstr ""
"Returns the prefill parameter configuration for all classes in the "
"workspace, including Agents and environment modules."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:7
#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:5 of
msgid "工作区根目录路径"
msgstr "Path to the workspace root directory."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:7 of
msgid ""
"Dict[str, Any]: 预填充参数配置，包含： - success: 是否成功 - data: 参数数据，结构为： - version: "
"配置版本 - env_modules: 环境模块预填充参数字典 - agents: Agent预填充参数字典"
msgstr ""
"Dict[str, Any]: Prefill parameter configuration, including: - success: "
"whether the request succeeded - data: parameter data, structured as: - "
"version: configuration version - env_modules: dictionary of prefill "
"parameters for environment modules - agents: dictionary of prefill "
"parameters for Agents"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:10
#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:8 of
msgid "500 - 读取配置文件失败"
msgstr "500 - Failed to read the configuration file"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_prefill_params:10 of
msgid "如果配置文件不存在，返回空配置结构。"
msgstr ""
"Returns an empty configuration structure if the configuration file does "
"not exist."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:1 of
msgid "获取特定类的预填充参数"
msgstr "Get prefill parameters for a specific class"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:3 of
msgid "返回指定类（Agent或环境模块）的预填充参数配置。"
msgstr ""
"Returns the prefill parameter configuration for the specified class, "
"either an Agent or an environment module."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:5 of
msgid "类类型，可选值： - env_module: 环境模块 - agent: Agent类"
msgstr ""
"Class kind. Available values: - env_module: environment module - agent: "
"Agent class"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:6 of
msgid "类名，如 mobility_space, basic_agent 等"
msgstr "Class name, such as mobility_space, basic_agent, and so on."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:9 of
msgid ""
"Dict[str, Any]: 类的预填充参数，包含： - success: 是否成功 - class_kind: 类类型 - "
"class_name: 类名 - params: 该类的预填充参数字典（如无配置则为空字典）"
msgstr ""
"Dict[str, Any]: Prefill parameters for the class, including: - success: "
"whether the request succeeded - class_kind: class kind - class_name: "
"class name - params: prefill parameter dictionary for the class, or an "
"empty dictionary when no configuration exists"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:13 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Examples"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params:14 of
msgid ""
"GET /api/v1/prefill-"
"params/env_module/mobility_space?workspace_path=/path/to/workspace"
msgstr ""
"GET /api/v1/prefill-"
"params/env_module/mobility_space?workspace_path=/path/to/workspace"

