"环境模块类字典，键为类型名，值为： - type: 类型名 - class_name: 类名 - description: 描述 - "
"is_custom: 是否为自定义模块 - count: 模块类总数"
msgstr ""
"Dict[str, Any]: Response containing environment module class information:"
" - success: whether the operation succeeded - modules: dictionary of "
"environment module classes, keyed by type name, with values containing: -"
" type: type name - class_name: class name - description: description - "
"is_custom: whether it is a custom module - count: total number of module "
"classes"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.modules.get_env_module_classes:8 of
msgid "500 - 获取环境模块类失败"
msgstr "500 - Failed to get environment module classes"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.modules.get_all_modules:1 of
