#: ../../api/backend.rst:52
msgid "Agent Skills 路由"
msgstr "Agent Skills Routing"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills:1 of
msgid "Agent Skills API 路由"
msgstr "Agent Skills API routing"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills:3 of
msgid "提供 agent skill 的列表、扫描自定义 skill、导入/创建/上传 skill 的 API 端点。"
msgstr ""
"API endpoints that provide a list of agent skills, enable/disable, scan "
"for custom skills, and import/create/upload skills."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills:5 of
msgid ""
"本路由基于 v2 skill 注册表 (:mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base.registry`)，它是一个 "
"**只读元数据注册表**：skill 是\"始终存在\"的目录，PersonAgent 在运行时按目录选择激活。 因此本路由**没有** "
"enable/disable/reload/remove 端点（v2 模型无此概念）。"
msgstr ""
"This route is based on the v2 skill registry "
"(:mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base.registry`), a **read-only metadata "
"registry**: skills are directories that always exist, and ``PersonAgent``"
" selects which ones to activate at runtime from the catalog. Therefore "
"this route has **no** enable / disable / reload / remove endpoints; those"
" concepts do not exist in the v2 model."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills:9 of
msgid ""
"关联文件： - @packages/agentsociety2/agentsociety2/agent/base/registry.py - "
"Skill 注册表 - @extension/src/apiClient.ts - VSCode 扩展 API 客户端 - "
"@frontend/src/pages/Skills/index.tsx - Web 前端 Skill 管理页"
msgstr ""
"Associated files: - "
"@packages/agentsociety2/agentsociety2/agent/skills/__init__.py - Skill "
"registry - @extension/src/apiClient.ts - VSCode extension API client - "
"@frontend/src/pages/Skills/index.tsx - Web front-end Skill management "
"page"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills:14 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"API 端点： - GET  /api/v1/agent-skills/list       — 列出所有已发现的 agent skill"
"（built-in + custom + env） - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/scan       — 扫描 "
"workspace/custom/skills/ 下的自定义 skill - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/import"
"     — 从路径导入 skill 目录 - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/create     — 在线创建新 "
"skill（SKILL.md + 可选脚本） - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/upload     — 上传 zip "
"包导入 skill - GET  /api/v1/agent-skills/{skill_id}/info — 获取 SKILL.md 内容"
msgstr ""
"API endpoints: - GET /api/v1/agent-skills/list - List all agent skills - "
"POST /api/v1/agent-skills/enable - Enable skill (enter optional "
"directory) - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/disable - Disable skill - POST "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/scan - Scan for custom skills under "
"workspace/custom/skills/ - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/import - Import "
"skill directory from path - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/create - Create new"
" skill online (SKILL.md + optional script) - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/upload - Upload zip package to import skill - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/reload - Hot reload specified skill - GET /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/{name}/info — Get SKILL.md content - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/remove — Remove custom skill"

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.list_skills:1 of
msgid "列出所有已发现的 Agent Skill（built-in + custom + env）。"
msgstr "List all discovered Agent Skills (builtin + custom + env)."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.scan_custom_skills:1 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "扫描工作区的自定义 Agent Skill（{workspace}/custom/skills/）。"
msgstr "Scan the workspace for custom Agent Skills ({workspace}/custom/skills/)."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.import_skill:1 of
msgid "从外部路径导入 Agent Skill（复制到 custom/skills/）。"
msgstr "Import Agent Skills from an external path (copied to custom/skills/)."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.create_skill:1 of
msgid "在线创建新的自定义 Skill。"
msgstr "Create new custom skills online."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.create_skill:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "在 custom/skills/{name}/ 下生成 SKILL.md（+ 可选脚本文件）。"
msgstr "Generate SKILL.md (+ optional script file) under custom/skills/{name}/."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.upload_skill:1 of
msgid "上传 zip 包导入 Skill。"
msgstr "Upload the zip package to import Skill."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.upload_skill:3 of
msgid "zip 包应包含一个顶层目录，内含 SKILL.md。"
msgstr "The zip package should contain a top-level directory containing SKILL.md."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.get_skill_info:1 of
msgid "获取 Skill 的详细信息（含 SKILL.md 内容）。"
msgstr "Get Skill details (including SKILL.md content)."

#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.agent_skills.get_skill_info:3 of
msgid ""
"``skill_id`` 形如 ``built-in@daily-guidance`` 或 ``custom@my-skill``，由 "
":meth:`SkillRegistry.list_all` 返回。"
msgstr ""
"``skill_id`` values look like ``built-in@daily-guidance`` or ``custom@my-"
"skill`` and are returned by :meth:`SkillRegistry.list_all`."

