#: agentsociety2.config.Config.EMBEDDING_DIMS:1 of
msgid "Dimensionality of the embedding vectors produced by the embedding model."
msgstr "Dimensionality of the embedding vectors produced by the embedding model."

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.EMBEDDING_DIMS:3 of
msgid "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_EMBEDDING_DIMS Default: 1024"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_EMBEDDING_DIMS Default: 1024"

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.EMBEDDING_DIMS:6 of
msgid ""
"This specifies the size of the vector space for embeddings. Higher "
"dimensions can capture more nuanced semantic information but require more"
" storage and computation. The value must match the actual output "
"dimensionality of the selected embedding model. Common values are 384, "
"512, 768, 1024, or 1536 depending on the model."
msgstr ""
"This specifies the size of the vector space for embeddings. Higher "
"dimensions can capture more nuanced semantic information but require more"
" storage and computation. The value must match the actual output "
"dimensionality of the selected embedding model. Common values are 384, "
"512, 768, 1024, or 1536 depending on the model."

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_LATENCY_DEGRADE_FACTOR:1 of
msgid ""
"Relative latency backoff factor for AIMD. A non-error LLM call is counted"
" as \"slow\" (and contributes to an AIMD decrease) when its latency "
"exceeds ``baseline * factor``, where ``baseline`` is a rolling low-"
"percentile (P25) of recent healthy latencies."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_LATENCY_DEGRADE_FACTOR:6 of
msgid "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_LATENCY_DEGRADE_FACTOR Default: 4.0"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_MODEL Default: \"gpt-5.5\""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_LATENCY_DEGRADE_FACTOR:9 of
msgid ""
"The baseline tracks the fast path, so this triggers when calls are "
"genuinely slow relative to recent good performance — robust to the "
"initial concurrent burst. Set to a very large value (or ``inf``) to "
"disable relative latency backoff and rely on rate-limit (429) errors "
"alone (the previous behavior)."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_SLOW_LATENCY_MS:1 of
msgid ""
"Optional absolute SLO ceiling in milliseconds. A non-error LLM call "
"slower than this counts as \"slow\" regardless of the rolling baseline. "
"Catches pathological tails even when sustained contention has pushed the "
"whole baseline up (where the relative factor goes blind)."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_SLOW_LATENCY_MS:6 of
msgid ""
"Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_SLOW_LATENCY_MS Default: unset "
"(relative-factor backoff only)"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_MODEL Default: \"gpt-5.5\""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_ROUND_SAMPLE_CAP:1 of
msgid ""
"Upper bound on AIMD round size (completions evaluated per adjustment). "
"Without this cap, round size grows with the limit, so a large limit makes"
" adaptation sluggish (e.g. limit 400 → 400 completions before any "
"adjust)."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_ROUND_SAMPLE_CAP:5 of
msgid "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_ROUND_SAMPLE_CAP Default: 64"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_MODEL Default: \"gpt-5.5\""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_WORKERS:1 of
msgid "Compatibility CPU-budget hint for Ray initialization."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_WORKERS:3 of
msgid "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_RAY_WORKERS Default: 1"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_MODEL Default: \"gpt-5.5\""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_WORKERS:6 of
msgid ""
"Kept for compatibility with older configs. The current LLM dispatcher "
"does not create a central pool or LLM actor workers; this value only "
"contributes to the ``ray.init(num_cpus=...)`` budget hint."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_MAX_WORKERS:1 of
msgid "Upper bound used as a Ray CPU budget hint."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_MAX_WORKERS:3 of
msgid "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_RAY_MAX_WORKERS Default: 4"
msgstr "Environment variable: AGENTSOCIETY_LLM_MODEL Default: \"gpt-5.5\""

#: agentsociety2.config.Config.LLM_RAY_MAX_WORKERS:6 of
msgid ""
"Used as the ``num_cpus`` hint to ``ray.init`` so env actors and agent Ray"
