msgstr "CodeGenRouter"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter:1 of
msgid "代码生成式Router：通过生成Python代码的方式调用环境模块中的@tool标记的接口。"
msgstr ""
"Code-generating Router: Calls the @tool-marked interface in the "
"environment module by generating Python code."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 使用类似 pyi 文件的 Python 代码格式向 LLM 提供环境模块描述和工具信息（含 "
"pydantic BaseModel 与模块类定义） 3. LLM 生成 Python 代码来调用工具 4. 使用 AST 解析检查代码安全性 "
"5. 通过 compile 和 exec 执行代码，捕获打印输出 6. 根据执行结果和打印输出生成最终响应"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information of all environment modules 2. "
"Provide environment module description and tool information (including "
"pydantic BaseModel and module class definition) to LLM using a Python "
"code format similar to pyi files 3. LLM generates Python code to call "
"tools 4. Use AST parsing to check code safety 5. Execute code through "
"compile and exec, capture printout 6. Generate final response based on "
"execution results and printout"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:1 of
msgid "使用代码生成方式处理指令。通过管道-过滤器架构执行。"
msgstr ""
"Use code generation to process instructions. Execution via pipe-filter "
"architecture."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:3 of
msgid "上下文字典（在template模式下，应包含'variables'键）"
msgstr "Context dictionary (in template mode, should contain the 'variables' key)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:4 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "指令字符串（在template模式下，为模板指令，包含{variable_name}占位符）"
msgstr ""
"Instruction string (in template mode, it is a template instruction, "
"including {variable_name} placeholder)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:6 of
msgid "是否启用模板模式（启用后使用缓存机制）"
msgstr "Whether to enable template mode (use caching mechanism after enabling)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.init:1 of
msgid ""
"Initialize the router with the start datetime and generate code using "
"LLM. 从本地缓存数据库加载当前 env 类型的缓存集，构建 FAISS 索引。"
msgstr ""
"Initialize the router with the start datetime and generate code using "
"LLM. Load the cache set of the current env type from the local cache "
"database and build the FAISS index."

