#: ../../api/skills.rst:92
msgid "SKILL.md Frontmatter"
msgstr "SKILL.md Frontmatter"

#: ../../api/skills.rst:94
msgid "SKILL.md 文件使用 YAML frontmatter 声明 skill 元信息："
msgstr "The SKILL.md file uses YAML frontmatter to declare skill metainformation:"

#: ../../api/skills.rst:106
msgid ""
"frontmatter 之后识别的字段：``name``、``description``（选择阶段唯一可见，决定是否激活）、 可选的 "
"``script``（默认脚本相对路径）与 ``hooks``（生命周期脚本映射，键如 ``pre_step`` / "
"``post_step``）。Skill 注册 id 形如 ``namespace@name``（内置 ``built-in@``、自定义 "
"``custom@``）。 脚本默认在 agent 进程内经 ``entrypoint(argv, ctx)`` 执行（详见 "
":doc:`/agent_skills`）；以 ``env:`` 开头的 skill id 会被重定向到 "
"``ask_env``，走环境路由而非脚本。"
msgstr ""
"Recognized frontmatter fields are ``name``, ``description`` (the only "
"text visible during selection and what determines activation), optional "
"``script`` (default relative script path), and ``hooks`` (lifecycle "
"script mapping with keys such as ``pre_step`` / ``post_step``). Skill "
"registration ids look like ``namespace@name`` (built-in ``built-in@``, "
"custom ``custom@``). Scripts execute by default in the agent process "
"through ``entrypoint(argv, ctx)`` (see :doc:`/agent_skills`); skill ids "
"starting with ``env:`` are redirected to ``ask_env`` and go through "
"environment routing rather than script execution."

#: ../../api/society.rst:2
msgid "Society 模块"
msgstr "Society Module"

#: ../../api/society.rst:4
msgid "本模块提供仿真的核心编排器和辅助工具。"
msgstr ""
"This module provides the core orchestrator and auxiliary tools for the "
"simulation."

#: ../../api/society.rst:7
msgid "AgentSociety"
msgstr "AgentSociety"

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:1 of
msgid "Record-based 仿真编排器（不持有 agent 对象）。"
msgstr "Record-based simulation orchestrator that does not hold agent objects."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:3 of
msgid "AgentSociety 是框架的核心类，负责管理仿真生命周期："
msgstr ""
"AgentSociety is the core class of the framework and is responsible for "
"managing the simulation life cycle:"

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"持有 **agent_specs**（元数据：``{\"id\",\"profile\",\"config\"}``）与 "
"**agent_ids**， 绝不在主进程常驻 agent 对象。"
msgstr ""
"Holds **agent_specs** (metadata: ``{\"id\",\"profile\",\"config\"}``) and"
" **agent_ids**, and never keeps resident agent objects in the main "
"process."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:7 of
msgid ""
"``step`` 每 tick 切批提交 ``step_agent_batch`` Ray Task，跨 worker 并行；批内顺序执行 （每个"
" agent 是 LLM-bound，顺序无妨）。"
msgstr ""
"On every tick, ``step`` splits agents into batches and submits "
"``step_agent_batch`` Ray Tasks for parallel execution across workers. "
"Agents within a batch run sequentially; each agent is LLM-bound, so this "
"is acceptable."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:9 of
msgid ""
"``ask``/``intervene``/``run_questionnaire``/``dump`` 为低频外部查询，按需在主进程 "
"``from_workspace`` 重建目标 agent（workspace 在本地磁盘）。"
msgstr ""
"``ask`` / ``intervene`` / ``run_questionnaire`` / ``dump`` are low-"
"frequency external queries. They rebuild the target agent in the main "
"process with ``from_workspace`` on demand; the workspace is on local "
"disk."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety:12 of
msgid "Example::"
msgstr "Example::"

