#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"agent 元数据列表，每个形如 ``{\"id\": int, \"profile\": dict, \"config\": "
"dict}``。仅元数据，不在构造时实例化。"
msgstr ""
"Agent metadata list. Each item has the form ``{\"id\": int, \"profile\": "
"dict, \"config\": dict}``. This is metadata only; agents are not "
"instantiated during construction."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:5 of
msgid "agent 类名（经 registry 解析，如 ``\"PersonAgent\"``）。"
msgstr ""
"Agent class name resolved through the registry, such as "
"``\"PersonAgent\"``."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:6 of
msgid "环境路由器（in-process 或 ``EnvRouterProxy``）。"
msgstr "Environment router, either in-process or ``EnvRouterProxy``."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:7 of
msgid "仿真开始时间。"
msgstr "Simulation start time."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:8 of
msgid "运行目录（``run_dir/agents`` 为 agent workspaces 根）。"
msgstr "Run directory; ``run_dir/agents`` is the root for agent workspaces."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:9 of
msgid ""
"共享服务句柄（env / llm / trace / replay）。流式任务 处理必需——runner 任务通过它访问 LLM clients "
"/ env actor。提供时 :meth:`init` 直接复用；``close`` 关闭其中 trace/replay actor。"
msgstr ""
"Shared service handles (env / llm / trace / replay). Required for "
"streaming tasks: runner tasks use it to access LLM clients and the env "
"actor. When provided, :meth:`init` reuses it directly; ``close`` closes "
"its trace / replay actor."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:12 of
msgid "每 ``step_agent_batch`` Ray Task 处理的 agent 数（默认 256）。"
msgstr ""
"Number of agents handled by each ``step_agent_batch`` Ray Task; default "
"is 256."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.__init__:13 of
msgid "是否启用回放记录。"
msgstr "Whether to enable playback recording."

#: agentsociety2.society.AgentSociety.current_time:1 of
msgid "返回当前仿真时间。"
msgstr "Returns the current simulation time."

#: agentsociety2.society.AgentSociety.step_count:1 of
msgid "返回已执行的仿真步数。"
msgstr "Returns the number of executed simulation steps."

#: agentsociety2.society.AgentSociety.agent_ids:1 of
msgid "返回所有 agent id（不暴露 agent 对象）。"
msgstr "Return all agent ids without exposing agent objects."

#: agentsociety2.society.AgentSociety.agent_specs:1 of
