"Initialize: Ray / LLM dispatcher -> service_proxy -> replay -> batched "
"workspace creation -> env init."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.close:1 of
msgid "关闭：env router + service_proxy 的 trace/replay 句柄 + LLM dispatcher。"
msgstr ""
"Close: env router, trace / replay actors in service_proxy, and the LLM "
"dispatcher."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.step:1 of
msgid "推进一次仿真步：sync clock → 切批 step_agent_batch → env.step → 前进时钟。"
msgstr ""
"Advance one simulation step: sync clock -> batch into "
"``step_agent_batch`` -> ``env.step`` -> advance clock."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run:1 of
msgid "运行多步仿真。"
msgstr "Run multi-step simulations."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run:3 of
msgid "运行步数上限。"
msgstr "The upper limit of running steps."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run:4 of
msgid "每步时间跨度（秒）。"
msgstr "Time span per step (seconds)."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.ask:1 of
msgid "向仿真系统提问（由 helper 协调 agents/env 作答）。"
msgstr ""
"Ask questions to the simulation system (helper coordinates agents/env to "
"answer)."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.ask:3 of
msgid "问题文本。"
msgstr "Question text."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.ask:4 of
msgid "答案文本。"
msgstr "Answer text."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.intervene:1 of
msgid "对仿真进行干预（由 helper 协调执行）。"
msgstr "Intervene in the simulation (coordinated by a helper)."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.intervene:3 of
msgid "干预指令文本。"
msgstr "Intervention instruction text."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.intervene:4 of
msgid "执行结果/反馈文本。"
msgstr "Execution results/feedback text."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run_questionnaire:1 of
msgid "向目标 agents 发放问卷并返回结构化结果。"
msgstr "Send questionnaires to target agents and return structured results."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run_questionnaire:3 of
msgid ""
"目标 agent 按 id 切批，每批提交一个 ``questionnaire_agent_batch`` Ray Task （与 "
"``step`` 同款分布式批处理）：worker 进程内 ``from_workspace`` 重建本批 "
"agents、并发跑完整个问卷、``to_workspace`` 落盘，再返回结构化结果。失败的单个 agent 被隔离（不中断整批），与 "
"``step_agent_batch`` 的容错语义一致。"
msgstr ""
"Target agents are batched by id, and each batch submits one "
"``questionnaire_agent_batch`` Ray Task, using the same distributed batch "
"processing pattern as ``step``. Inside the worker process, "
"``from_workspace`` rebuilds the batch of agents, runs the full "
"questionnaire concurrently, persists with ``to_workspace``, and returns "
"structured results. A failed individual agent is isolated and does not "
"interrupt the whole batch, matching the fault-tolerance semantics of "
"``step_agent_batch``."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run_questionnaire:8 of
msgid "问卷定义。"
msgstr "Questionnaire definition."

#: agentsociety2.society.society.AgentSociety.run_questionnaire:9 of
