#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_sink.ReplayWriter:1 of
msgid "Back-compat alias over :class:`ReplaySink`."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_sink.ReplayWriter:3 of
msgid ""
"The legacy public API (:mod:`agentsociety2.storage`, examples) "
"constructed a SQLite writer with a ``.db`` file path and called ``await "
"init()`` before use. That writer is gone; this alias keeps the symbol "
"importable and writes the same JSONL format, mapping the legacy "
"``db_path`` to a replay directory (a trailing ``.db`` is stripped) so old"
" call sites keep working without SQLite."
msgstr ""

#: ../../api/storage.rst:15
msgid "ReplaySink"
msgstr "ReplayWriter"

