"One instance per writer process (driver / env router actor / each agent "
"Ray task). Holds its own open shard fds; ``flock`` makes concurrent "
"appends to the same shard file safe for rows of any size."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_sink.ReplaySink.init:1 of
