#: ../../api/storage.rst:51
msgid "分布式 Replay Proxy"
msgstr "Distributed Replay Proxy"

#: ../../api/storage.rst:53
msgid ""
"大规模仿真下，``ReplayProxy`` 只携带 ``replay_dir`` 与启用标志。各 agent / env / society "
"进程收到 proxy 后在本地懒加载 ``ReplaySink``，并直接 append sharded JSONL。"
msgstr ""
"In large-scale simulations, ``ReplayProxy`` only carries ``replay_dir`` "
"and the enabled flag. After each agent / env / society process receives "
"the proxy, it lazily loads a local ``ReplaySink`` and appends sharded "
"JSONL directly."

#: ../../api/storage.rst:57
msgid "ReplayProxy"
msgstr "ReplayWriter"

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_proxy.ReplayProxy:1 of
msgid "Serializable config for distributed replay writing."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_proxy.ReplayProxy:3 of
msgid ""
"Carries only the replay output directory and an enable flag — no Ray "
"actor handle. Methods lazily build+cache a process-local "
":class:`ReplaySink` (from ``replay_dir``) on first use and delegate, so "
"each agent Ray task / env actor that receives a deserialized copy gets "
"its own sink and its own file descriptors. ``enabled=False`` makes every "
"method a no-op."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_sink.build_replay_sink:1 of
msgid "Build a per-process :class:`ReplaySink` from a :class:`ReplayProxy`."
msgstr ""

#: agentsociety2.storage.replay_sink.build_replay_sink:3 of
msgid "Returns ``None`` when the proxy is disabled or carries no ``replay_dir``."
msgstr ""

